&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div></description></item><item><title>Lesson001 - 第一次看見色彩</title><link>https://blog.goldfishbrain-fighting.com/2023/voicetube-hero-learn-english-lesson001/</link><pubDate>Mon, 09 Oct 2023 21:44:08 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://blog.goldfishbrain-fighting.com/2023/voicetube-hero-learn-english-lesson001/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="學習影片">學習影片&lt;/h2>
